by SpacePossum at 2016-08-29T07:54:54Z

Isn't the problem here: https://github.com/FriendsOfPHP/PHP-CS-Fixer/pull/2162/files#diff-12b3be4cb17c0a53ac8a34fe6e2d8a2cR131

```php
        // ignore corrupted serialized data
        if (null === $data) {
            return;
        }
```

as
```php
$a = @unserialize(null);
var_dump($a);

$a = @unserialize('');
var_dump($a);
```

all give `false` and not `null`

